Package utilities

Class MyDLLNode

java.lang.Object
utilities.MyDLLNode
public class MyDLLNode
extends java.lang.Object
MyDLLNode.java - implements a Doubly Linked List node. This node consists of an element and two links: to its successor and predecessor.
Version:
March 10, 2021
Author:
Jaehan Kim, Donghyun Kim, Maria Laura Diaz Pena
